Solve 5 business problems with different ML techniques:
1. HR Department: predict employee churn rate with ANN, SMOTE & Logistic Regression Classifier;
2. Marketing Department: divide customers into 3 clusters for targeted ad campaign with k-means & autoencoder;
3. Sales Department: predict future faily sales given store features with time-series, FB Prophet, additive regression & trends;
4. Operations Department: detect and classify chest disease given X-ray images with CNN, ResNet & Transfer Learning;
5. PR Department: predict customer satisfaction on product with NLP, sentiment analysis & Naive Bayes Classifier.
